## ğŸ¤– Simple Chatbot

```elixir
defmodule ChatBot do
  def respond(message) do
    cond do
      String.contains?(String.downcase(message), "hello") ->
        "Hello! How are you?"

      String.contains?(String.downcase(message), "good") ->
        "I'm glad! How can I help you?"

      String.contains?(String.downcase(message), "bye") ->
        "See you later! ğŸ‘‹"

      true ->
        "Interesting... tell me more."
    end
  end
end

ChatBot.respond("Hello robot")
```

